<header>
<div class="blogparent"><a href="../words" rel="tag">Words</a>:</div>
<h1>You're a Wizard, Harry.</h1>
<small>December 4, 2018</small>
</header>

<p>
4 words.<br>
4 words that we all wish we could hear.<br>
4 words that would answer the question we all ask.<br>
4 words that represent the greatest gift you could give.
</p><p>
4 words that most of us don’t hear.<br>
4 words that most don’t feel qualified to say.<br>
4 words that give the gift of certainty.<br>
4 words that spark a dream inside you.
</p><p>
4 words that are all too easy to say.<br>
4 words that feel impossible to mean.<br>
4 words that literally give the blueprint to move mountains.<br>
4 words that give the power to motivate countries.
</p><p>
4 words that a family member had the stones to say to me.<br>
4 words that have haunted me since that very day.<br>
4 words I can’t get out of my head.<br>
4 words that opened the door to me writing this very word.
</p>

